snippet.title: MY HERO ULTRA RUMBLE — Open Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
💥MY HERO ULTRA RUMBLE is back! 💥
Join the action May 25th – June 1st, only on PlayStation 4!

The following characters are playable in the #MHUR Open Beta Test:

New:
💨Tenya Iida
💥Denki Kaminari
🛡️Itsuka Kendo 

Returning:
🛡️Midoriya Izuku
💥Bakugo Katsuki
🍥Uraraka Ochaco
💥Todoroki Shoto
💨Tsuyu Asui
🛡️All Might
💚Cementoss
🛡️Mt. Lady
💥Tomura Shigaraki
🍥Dabi
💨Himiko Toga
💚Mr. Compress

Pre-install the Open Beta today: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP0700-CUSA32899_00-HEROVSGAMEOBT000

#MYHEROULTRARUMBLE #MHUR
Follow MY HERO ULTRA RUMBLE:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/myherour/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MyHeroUR
